original: Ek, Ejnar Karl Axel, civilingenjör, Visby, f. 2/2/14 i Nyköping. G. 36 m. Anna Lisa Gustafsson. Barn: Torsten f. 36, Torbjörn 40, Lennart 42. — Stud:ex. i Nyköp. 35, civ:ing:ex. v. KTH 39. E. bitr. ing. v. väg- o. vat-tenbyggn :styr. 39-43, ing. v. vägför-valtn. i Gotl. 1. sed. 44. Hobby: musik (piano).
translated: Ek, Ejnar Karl Axel, engineer, Visby, b. February 2, 1914 in Nyköping. Married in 1936 to Anna Lisa Gustafsson. Children: Torsten b. 1936, Torbjörn b. 1940, Lennart b. 1942. - Received a high school diploma in Nyköping in 1935, a engineering diploma from KTH in 1939. Worked as assistant engineer for the Road and Water Construction Board from 1939-1943, and as an engineer for the Road Administration in Gotland since 1944. Hobby: music (piano).
